    public final class ConceptParentAdapter
extends org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.impl.AdapterImpl
    Customized adapter wrapping a bunch of SNOMED CT concept IDs.
    This adapter should be used for hierarchy building for *NOT* persisted SNOMED CT concepts.
